This directory holds the SQLCipher Community Edition amalgamation
(`sqlite3.c` and `sqlite3.h`) used as the storage engine for this fork of
WatermelonDB. Encryption-at-rest is mandatory; the SQLite library shipped in
upstream WatermelonDB at `@nozbe/sqlite` does not include the SQLCipher
codec and is intentionally not used here.

