  https://github.com/sqlcipher/sqlcipher/blob/master/LICENSE

The amalgamation sources are NOT committed to this repository. They are
generated on demand by `scripts/vendor-sqlcipher.sh` (which runs
automatically via the `postinstall` npm hook) or can be downloaded from the
official SQLCipher release tarballs. The pinned version is recorded in
`scripts/vendor-sqlcipher.sh`.

